# GitHub OAuth Configuration
# This is optional. If not set, users can still use the app with manual tokens or without authentication.

# To enable GitHub OAuth Device Flow:
# 1. Go to https://github.com/settings/applications/new
# 2. Fill in the application details:
#    - Application name: IssueVista
#    - Homepage URL: http://localhost:4321 (or your production URL)
#    - Application description: Find unassigned GitHub issues without PRs
#    - Authorization callback URL: Not needed for device flow
# 3. Click "Register application"
# 4. Copy the "Client ID" and paste it below

PUBLIC_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=your_github_client_id_here
